r class. Some will believe that SOE doesn't care. Some will believe that SOE thinks that their concerns are too trivial to bother with. Some will believe that their concerns are not even being reviewed by SOE employees. No matter what they believe continued silence will only reinforce their belief. This continued negative feedback at best will engender suspicion of SOE's motives.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As for the in-game feedback command? Why should that work any better than these boards?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
